# source:   athena
# purpose:  Lockfile install version drift -- compares >= floors in
#           pyproject.toml against lockfile pins. Reports deps where the lock
#           has drifted far ahead of the declared minimum.
# baseline: Current drift state. Changes indicate new drift or bumped floors
#           requiring acknowledgment.
# columns:  lockfile	package	drift_type	drift_count	floor	lock_version
requirements-dev.lock	mypy	MAJOR	1	1.5	2.1.0
requirements-dev.lock	pytest	MAJOR	2	7.0	9.1.1
